AUDIO: 'photography. Photos often look nicer if you have a shallow depth of field, or in other words, if the background looks blurriier. That way, the subject would stand out and the image would look more 3D. And I\'ve been waiting for a long'

[11:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'time for an AI to be able to control this bouquet effect. So, finally, this is it. Here are some examples of this in action. If you keep the same prompt and all the other settings the same, but you'

